# 📢 Recipe Viewer - Release Notes

## 🚀 Version 1.0.0 (Initial Release)
### 🎉 What's Here:
- **Recipe Extraction:** Automatically detects and extracts only the necessary recipe details (title, ingredients, instructions, and cooking time).
- **Minimalist Display:** Removes unnecessary content like blog stories, ads, and other clutter
- **Wide Compatibility:** Works with popular recipe websites.
- **User-Friendly Interface:** Simple and clean layout for easy reading.
- **Manual Override:** Allows users to refresh extraction if needed.

### 🛠️ Installation & Usage:
Follow the steps outlined in the [README](https://github.com/janwils/RecipeExtension/blob/main/README.md) to install and use the extension.

### 🐞 Known Issues:
- Some websites with complex structures may not extract perfectly.
- Minor UI inconsistencies on certain webpages.

### 📩 Feedback:
We'd love to hear your thoughts! Report any bugs or suggest improvements on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/janwils/RecipeExtension/issues)
[Feedback Form](https://forms.gle/LBM9ezRH9ubD1LQa9).

---
Happy Cooking! 🍽️🎉
